169
00:13:31,186 --> 00:13:33,605
That's why, as his grandson,
I'm going to protect it!

170
00:13:33,939 --> 00:13:36,483
Fool! This isn't the time for that!

171
00:13:36,566 --> 00:13:38,902
The Leaf Village is in great danger!

172
00:13:38,985 --> 00:13:42,030
So what?! It doesn't matter to me.

173
00:13:42,989 --> 00:13:44,199
Are you seriously saying that?!

174
00:13:47,410 --> 00:13:49,704
Oh, now I'm mad!

175
00:13:49,788 --> 00:13:54,918
