a great Ninja he was,

198
00:16:25,735 --> 00:16:28,321
they're just going to put him away
like an old ashtray.

199
00:16:29,572 --> 00:16:33,535
The new Hokage will make all kinds
of changes in the Leaf Village.

200
00:16:34,119 --> 00:16:35,829
That's not true!

201
00:16:35,912 --> 00:16:37,622
The Hidden Leaf Village is
the Hidden Leaf Village.

202
00:16:37,706 --> 00:16:41,292
And besides,
nobody will forget about the Old Man!

203
00:16:41,376 --> 00:16:43,503
No! They will never forget about him!

204
00:16:44,713 --> 00:16:47,048
They will forget, I guarantee it.

205
00:16:47,632 --> 00:16:49,592
-They won't forget!
-That's a lie!

206
00:16:49,676 --> 00:16:53,054
It's not a lie!
You can't believe what I am saying?!

207
00:16:53,471 --> 00:16:54,514
That's right, I can't!

208
00:16:54,597 --> 00:16:57,016
Oh boy!

209
00:16:57,392 --> 00:16:59,310
Come with me, Konohamaru!

210
00:16:59,394 --> 00:17:01,521
We just have to get Old Lady Tsunade
to promise

211
00:17:01,604 --> 00:17:04,107
that she won't change
the Village Hidden in the Leaves.

212
00:17:04,190 --> 00:17:05,400
And then on top of that,

213
00:17:05,483 --> 00:17:08,236
we can get everybody to promise us
that they won't forget about the Old Man!

214
00:17:08,695 --> 00:17:09,738
What?

215
00:17:10,238 --> 00:17:11,990
Isn't that what you want?

216
00:17:18,329 --> 00:17:22,542
I can't believe that I let
Lady Tsunade out of my sight!

217
00:17:29,215 --> 00:17:30,592
Did you find her, Tonton?

218
00:17:45,231 --> 00:17:47,692
Revitalizing the cells, I see.

219
00:17:56,826 --> 00:18:00,038
-I've found you Lady Tsunade.
-What?

220
00:18:04,375 --> 00:18:07,420
Lady Tsunade is studying?!

221
00:18:07,879 --> 00:18:10,632
Be quiet! I can't concentrate.

222
00:18:12,258 --> 00:18:13,301
Concentrate?!

223
00:18:13,802 --> 00:18:16,971
I've never heard you use that word
except when you're gambling.

224
00:18:17,764 --> 00:18:19,766
Is that Shizune's voice?

225
00:18:20,225 --> 00:18:21,976
Shizune...

226
00:18:24,771 --> 00:18:27,732
Do you remember that Medical Ninja
by the name of Kabuto?

227
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:34,113
-What about him?
-His ability to create new cells.

228
00:18:34,197 --> 00:18:37,158
I was researching ways to use
that power on the patients.

229
00:18:38,368 --> 00:18:39,869
For Lee?

230
00:18:40,453 --> 00:18:46,835
If the 50% chance becomes 51%,
it's worth a try.

231
00:18:47,168 --> 00:18:51,339
It really depends on the individual's traits.

232
00:18:51,923 --> 00:18:55,385
Even for you,
it might be hard to acquire those powers.

233
00:18:58,763 --> 00:19:00,265
I'll just have to try.

234
00:19:02,267 --> 00:19:04,769
I am the Fifth Hokage, after all.

235
00:19:14,070 --> 00:19:16,865
It can't be helped, Konohamaru.

236
00:19:17,574 --> 00:19:20,493
I am the Third Hokage, after all.

237
00:19:20,577 --> 00:19:23,329
If you don't like it,
you should just quit!

238
00:19:24,455 --> 00:19:27,417
Everybody from the village is my family.

239
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:31,296
To protect the family,
that is the duty of a Hokage.

240
00:19:33,548 --> 00:19:35,800
Oh! Old Man!

241
00:19:50,356 --> 00:19:52,859
Just for today,
I'm making a special exception.

242
00:19:57,447 --> 00:19:59,282
What's the matter Konohamaru?

243
00:19:59,365 --> 00:20:02,076
Don't you want to see Old Lady Tsunade?

244
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:03,286
No.

245
00:20:11,961 --> 00:20:16,549
I'll just have to do it.
I am the Fifth Hokage, after all.

246
00:20:16,633 --> 00:20:21,804
It can't be helped, Konohamaru.
I am the Third Hokage, after all.

247
00:20:23,348 --> 00:20:27,143
It can't be helped.
I am the honorable grandson, after all.

248
00:20:27,602 --> 00:20:28,603
Huh?

249
00:20:29,020 --> 00:20:32,482
I am Konohamaru of
the Hidden Leaf Village, after all!

250
00:20:32,815 --> 00:20:36,611
H-Hey Konohamaru, wait!

251
00:20:36,694 --> 00:20:40,865
What's going on with him? Hey Konohamaru!

252
00:20:46,913 --> 00:20:49,457
-Lady Tsunade?
-Nothing...

253
00:21:05,556 --> 00:21:09,519
I believe your promise,
its a true heart give me courage

254
00:21:09,602 --> 00:21:14,983
Always I feel it
the precious time with you

255
00:21:15,066 --> 00:21:19,821
On your still shoulder

256
00:21:19,904 --> 00:21:24,492
I feel the wind that blows
towards tomorrow

257
00:21:24,575 --> 00:21:30,415
The city lights are like pieces of stars

258
00:21:30,498 --> 00:21:35,086
That hold us together

259
00:21:35,169 --> 00:21:39,507
"Each one of us

260
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:44,512
glows differently,"

261
00:21:44,595 --> 00:21:47,348
you say laughingly

262
00:21:47,432 --> 00:21:53,688
but you look most dazzling

263
00:21:53,771 --> 00:21:58,234
Like a comet,

264
00:21:58,317 --> 00:22:04,157
like the rainbow after the storm

265
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:08,870
You bring light

266
00:22:08,953 --> 00:22:11,456
into my heart

267
00:22:12,540 --> 00:22:16,878
Being lost

268
00:22:16,961 --> 00:22:22,467
can be the answer

269
00:22:23,092 --> 00:22:28,306
Let's promise

270
00:22:28,389 --> 00:22:31,017
we won't cheat

271
00:22:31,100 --> 00:22:35,021
Uh...like a shooting star, we do go ahead.

272
00:22:37,607 --> 00:22:39,692
Back then, Sensei taught me

273
00:22:39,776 --> 00:22:43,529
that I would grow up to become
a great Ninja

274
00:22:43,613 --> 00:22:46,991
through lots of effort and
competition with my rivals.

275
00:22:47,075 --> 00:22:48,951
His words put me at ease.

276
00:22:49,035 --> 00:22:52,538
A path opened up for me
just when I was unsure of myself.

277
00:22:53,206 --> 00:22:55,374
I realized that all I had to do
was try my best.

278
00:22:56,292 --> 00:22:57,460
But now...

279
00:22:57,543 --> 00:23:01,839
Next time: "Sensei and Student:
The Bond of the Shinobi"

